  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the scrambled tofu and cook until lightly browned, breaking up with a spatula as needed.",
    "Add the cooked jasmine rice to the pan, stirring to combine with the tofu.",
    "Add the fried shallots, miso paste, brown sugar, and soy sauce to the pan, stirring until the mixture is well combined and heated through.",
    "Divide the mixture among the scallop shells, topping each with chopped scallions.",
    "Serve the plump British jelly hash hot, garnished with additional scallions if desired."
